         <p class="capture">六曜も表示<br /><a href="./images/captures/ja/capture5.png"><img width="240px" src="./images/captures/ja/capture5_s.png" /></a></p>
         <p class="capture">カレンダーの色はどんな色にでも<br /><a href="./images/captures/ja/capture6.png"><img width="240px" src="./images/captures/ja/capture6_s.png" /></a></p>
